# ЁЯПл Backend API тАУ SMA Budi Mulia

Backend Express.js + MongoDB untuk sistem manajemen jadwal & materi SMA Budi Mulia.

---

## ЁЯЪА Cara Menjalankan

### 1. Install dependencies
```bash
npm install
```

### 2. Buat file `.env`
Copy dari `.env.example` lalu isi dengan nilai asli:
```bash
cp .env.example .env
```

### 3. Jalankan server
```bash
npm run dev      # development (pakai nodemon)
npm start        # production
```

Server berjalan di: `http://localhost:5000`

---

## ЁЯУд Cara Push ke GitHub

```bash
# 1. Masuk ke folder project
cd budi_mulia_backend-main

# 2. Init git (kalau belum pernah)
git init

# 3. Tambahkan semua file (node_modules & .env sudah di .gitignore)
git add .

# 4. Commit
git commit -m "feat: implementasi API admin (CRUD user, jadwal, pengumuman)"

# 5. Hubungkan ke repo GitHub (ganti URL dengan repo kalian)
git remote add origin https://github.com/username/nama-repo.git

# 6. Push
git push -u origin main
```

> тЪая╕П File `.env` **tidak** akan ter-push karena sudah ada di `.gitignore`

---

## ЁЯУЛ Daftar API Endpoint

### ЁЯФР Auth
| Method | Endpoint | Deskripsi |
|--------|----------|-----------|
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | Login user |

**Body login:**
```json
{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "password123"
}
```

---

### ЁЯСе Admin тАУ User Management
> Semua endpoint butuh header: `Authorization: Bearer <token>`

| Method | Endpoint | Deskripsi |
|--------|----------|-----------|
| GET | `/api/admin/users` | List semua user (siswa & guru) |
| GET | `/api/admin/users/:id` | Detail 1 user |
| POST | `/api/admin/users` | Buat user baru |
| PUT | `/api/admin/users/:id` | Update user |
| DELETE | `/api/admin/users/:id` | Hapus user |

**Query params GET /users:**
- `role=siswa` atau `role=guru`
- `search=nama` тАФ cari by nama/username
- `page=1&limit=20` тАФ pagination

**Body POST/PUT user:**
```json
{
  "nama": "Budi Santoso",
  "username": "budi.santoso",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "siswa",
  "nisn": "1234567890",
  "kelas": "10 B"
}
```
Untuk guru:
```json
{
  "nama": "Pak Ahmad",
  "username": "pak.ahmad",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "guru",
  "nip": "198501012010011001",
  "mapel": "Matematika"
}
```

---

### ЁЯУЕ Admin тАУ Jadwal
| Method | Endpoint | Deskripsi |
|--------|----------|-----------|
| GET | `/api/admin/jadwal` | List jadwal |
| POST | `/api/admin/jadwal/save` | Simpan/timpa jadwal |

**Body POST jadwal/save:**
```json
{
  "kelas": "10 B",
  "tahunAjaran": "2024/2025",
  "durasi": 45,
  "jadwal": {
    "Senin": {
      "1": { "mapel": "Matematika", "guru": "Pak Ahmad" },
      "2": { "mapel": "Fisika", "guru": "Bu Sari" }
    },
    "Selasa": {}
  }
}
```

---

### ЁЯУв Admin тАУ Pengumuman
| Method | Endpoint | Deskripsi |
|--------|----------|-----------|
| GET | `/api/admin/pengumuman` | List pengumuman |
| POST | `/api/admin/pengumuman` | Buat pengumuman |
| PUT | `/api/admin/pengumuman/:id` | Edit pengumuman |
| DELETE | `/api/admin/pengumuman/:id` | Hapus pengumuman |

**Body POST/PUT pengumuman:**
```json
{
  "judul": "Libur Hari Raya",
  "isi": "Sekolah libur tanggal 10-15 April 2025.",
  "tag": "Libur",
  "target": "semua",
  "penting": true
}
```
`target`: `"semua"` / `"siswa"` / `"guru"`

---

### ЁЯУК Admin тАУ Stats
| Method | Endpoint | Deskripsi |
|--------|----------|-----------|
| GET | `/api/admin/stats` | Jumlah siswa, guru, pengumuman, jadwal |
